{"id": 2346, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得国产剧哪些表现“国际化”的方式该更新换代了？", "description": "离别总在机场，她要飞去美国。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images  ）", "record_count": 3335, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180516172935XdqeCcGa3mLEQoFu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-31T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 285184, "content": "离别时候男主角突然发现其实还是很爱女主角吻了女主角女主角惊讶无比说你爱我吗男主角说我爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268640}, {"id": 284931, "content": "能别成天只和二战鬼子“来往”吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357899}, {"id": 284932, "content": "  剧本一个套路，无论前期什么剧情，最后总能扯到男女主的感情纠葛，就那么几个类型，还乐此不疲的拍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 284935, "content": "抱歉，我好多年都不看国产剧了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292131}, {"id": 285194, "content": "穷人女主穿的衣服用的包都是名牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362036}, {"id": 284939, "content": "情感剧，古装剧，医疗剧，商业剧，统统都是爱情剧！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310259}, {"id": 284940, "content": "一大堆不看国产剧的进来强答，真是非常的国产剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110037}, {"id": 285964, "content": "总有演技生涩的外国人群演，来表示“上流社会”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367614}, {"id": 284941, "content": "说点什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360731}, {"id": 284942, "content": "w", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360731}, {"id": 285198, "content": "总是有小三", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361957}, {"id": 284943, "content": "q", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360731}, {"id": 284944, "content": "l", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360731}, {"id": 284945, "content": "一言不合，就出国", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298871}, {"id": 284946, "content": "总得有一个人来插足男主和女主的爱情，基本上，都是这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 79816}, {"id": 284947, "content": "很low的ABC", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 284948, "content": "国产剧是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319595}, {"id": 284949, "content": "我也在想，我看了哪些国产剧……《亮剑》算不算？里面的国际化就是：打日本人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327163}, {"id": 284950, "content": "各地方言成为了凸显普通话倍儿流利男女主人公优越的陪衬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356268}, {"id": 284951, "content": "不管在哪女主的智商弱到令人发指最后都是靠男人拯救", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678350}, {"id": 284952, "content": "除了谈恋爱啥事也不会干。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678350}, {"id": 284953, "content": "一直看的美剧英剧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993133}, {"id": 287514, "content": "大概10年不看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778939}, {"id": 284956, "content": "只能有一个人说话？然后刚刚要说的事不小心被另一个人打断了就不说了。我真搞不懂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360822}, {"id": 284958, "content": "所谓的华尔街精英总裁满口Chinglish，出场一定要高贵冷艳喜欢区分阶级，回国之后莫名其妙有豪车开有豪宅住", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275571}, {"id": 284959, "content": "电视剧演员永远生活在电视剧里，跟生活无关，这个锅应该编剧背。哈哈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326256}, {"id": 285216, "content": "中英结合说话方式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322032}, {"id": 284962, "content": "题材匮乏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360920}, {"id": 285218, "content": "男女主总有一个会出国，然后多年后重逢；或者女主出国散心回国后逆袭；或者有些国外的上市公司给了故事人物一个成功的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344689}, {"id": 284963, "content": "没怎么看过。我觉得全部要换。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 284964, "content": "yay", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142742}, {"id": 284965, "content": "号称是海龟，业务能力却差到令人发指的做事迷迷糊糊的玛丽苏女主", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225209}, {"id": 285221, "content": "有什么国产剧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361750}, {"id": 284967, "content": "明明一句话就可以了，非得编出3集没营养的，看着容易得狂躁症。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360942}, {"id": 284968, "content": "看我的团长我的团里，那两个老美跟炮灰团就特别能融在一起。这估计还是得看剧本和角色内核的塑造的能力吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301376}, {"id": 284970, "content": "伪命题，文化属性！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360832}, {"id": 285226, "content": "房子都很整齐，却还要打扫。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294902}, {"id": 284971, "content": "伪命题，文化属性！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360832}, {"id": 284972, "content": "不看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315624}, {"id": 284973, "content": "找母语非英语的外国人来尬演。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092465}, {"id": 285229, "content": "什么都是爱情故事，没看到结局就能猜出来有两种。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224508}, {"id": 284975, "content": "大多数来自中上层的自嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189444}, {"id": 296244, "content": "停播国产剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342129}, {"id": 285240, "content": "关注自己土地上的事情，不要抄别国的这种国际化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363100}, {"id": 285008, "content": "海归说话总是中英混说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353028}, {"id": 285012, "content": "张三不叫张三，叫薇薇安张，可能现在也依然这样吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720470}, {"id": 285540, "content": "拿起手机打电话的时候炫外语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872774}, {"id": 285036, "content": "女主或男主出国回来秒变精英", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336267}, {"id": 286318, "content": "我觉得创意和背景单一有点像样板戏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369147}, {"id": 284785, "content": "不看国产剧的我不知怎么回答……", "image": null, "praise_count": 791, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288126}]}